{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM08_050.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "We weren't able to buy many vegetables..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "There are monsters near town, and the crops aren't growing well... Things seem really weird lately..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...I fear that the changes are likely caused by Luard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Huh? What do you mean?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Luard has likely resumed his Ablation Alchemy research. The changes you see recently are a result of that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Ablation... Alchemy? Is that different from regular alchemy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yes. As I explained before, the alchemy you and I use listens to the wishes of materials, and helps fulfill them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "...On the other hand, Ablation Alchemy ignores the wishes of materials, forcing them to morph into another form."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It ignores the wishes of materials to make things... Doesn't that mean you could create anything you wanted?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Isn't that actually a good thing? It would be really convenient."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You aren't mistaken that it's convenient. However, that convenience comes at an equivalent price."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "A price...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Alchemy that ignores the wishes of materials costs far more than normal alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "The cost in this case is the power of nature. Normally, the power of nature that we use slowly recovers."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "However, Ablation Alchemy uses that power at a faster rate than it can recover, wasting enormous amounts of it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "As a result, it eats away at nature little by little... Eventually, the power of nature would be exhausted."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I can't even imagine what would occur if that was to happen."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "The \"Scar of the Land\" was carved into the earth by the influence of Ablation Alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "The \"Scar of the Land\"...? I didn't know..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Yes. The changes you see recently are likely related to the power of nature slowly being consumed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "...It seems we really can't allow Luard to continue his Ablation Alchemy much longer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "If used carefully, it would probably be somewhat sustainable, but Luard makes no such effort."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "We need to figure out where Luard went as quickly as possible, and stop him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I'll keep working to improve my alchemy, for your memories too!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Yes, please do so."
        }
    ]
}